title: Lady Gaga (Full Interview) | Colbert Classic
description:
Stephen's wide-ranging conversation with superstar Lady Gaga covers everything from her Oscar-nominated performance in "A Star Is Born" to the national debate surrounding Brett Kavanaugh's appointment to the Supreme Court.
